<div class="d-r">
  <div class="s">Who Should Not Use KLOW</div>
  <p>Individuals with copper metabolism disorders (Wilson's disease) must avoid GHK-Cu entirely. Active cancer patients should not use growth-promoting peptides. Pregnant or breastfeeding women lack sufficient safety data. Anyone on blood thinners should consult their physician before starting, as some peptides may influence wound healing dynamics.</p>
</div>

